      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i've been working on this sourdough starter for like two weeks now and it's just not consistent. like some days it's super bubbly and active but then it just sits there and does nothing even though i'm keeping it at the same temp. what's actually going on with the yeast and the bacteria in there? why is it so unpredictable?",
