      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"vigorous little workers\" haha okay, i get it. but i'm more interested in the science part. since they're microorganisms, does the way they interact change based on the hydration level of the starter? like, if it's a liquidy starter vs a thick one, does that change how they move around or interact with each other?",
